WEBVTT

00:00:24.680 --> 00:00:30.047
And I believe the end product of it
will be entirely about engagement.

00:00:30.476 --> 00:00:34.609
In fact, I think it is possibly
a transformational change

00:00:34.633 --> 00:00:37.407
in the way we're going
to think about engagement.

00:00:37.431 --> 00:00:42.716
So what would you do if you knew today

00:00:43.978 --> 00:00:46.376
that there was going to be
a major technology cycle

00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:48.183
beginning in the next couple years,

00:00:48.207 --> 00:00:50.066
and that you could participate in it?

00:00:50.411 --> 00:00:52.472
What would you do?

00:00:52.789 --> 00:00:53.955
(Audience) Jump in!

00:00:53.979 --> 00:00:57.429
So, this is the situation
in which I find myself:

00:00:57.969 --> 00:01:01.013
I'm a professional investor
about half the day,